{"type": "article", "id": 28559, "title": "Balmain归了中东人，以及，王大仁为李宇春设计巡演服｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-06-22T11:02:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3835, "name": "瑞士"}, {"id": 1936, "name": "香水"}, {"id": 1705, "name": "腕表"}, {"id": 10501, "name": "剑桥包"}, {"id": 3313, "name": "洛杉矶"}, {"id": 393, "name": "收购"}, {"id": 9551, "name": "卡塔尔"}, {"id": 15043, "name": "YG"}, {"id": 10495, "name": "Cambridge Satchel"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 2002, "name": "Balmain"}, {"id": 9254, "name": "Bobbi Brown"}, {"id": 3340, "name": "Valentino"}, {"id": 1722, "name": "Alexander Wang"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 14, "praise_count": 71, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703124359Ipqi4fFmQA3bYVJg.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Qatar-fund-acquires-French-fashion-house-Balmain,706096.html\"><b>Valentino 东家收购 Balmain</b></a>｜2012 年收购华伦天奴（Valentino）的卡塔尔皇室投资基金 Mayhoola，已最终与巴黎品牌 Balmain 达成全资收购合约，据法国回声报报道，Mayhoola 将支付 4.85 亿欧元（约合 5.46 亿美元）。此前 Balmain 70% 的股份由前已逝 CEO Alain Hivelin 的继承人持有，余下 30% 在管理层手中。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/accessories-news/watches/swiss-watch-exports-fall-9-7-in-may-10463960/\"><b>瑞士手表五月出口额持续下跌</b></a>｜瑞士钟表工业联合会（Federation of the Swiss Watch Industry）报道，五月，瑞士钟表出口额下跌了 9.7%，受累于贵重金属材质的腕表主要市场销量急速下滑。而在此前，四月和三月的下跌幅度分别为 11.1% 和 16.1%。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/eye/fashion/alexander-wang-chris-lee-li-yuchun-why-me-tour-10464346/\"><b>王大仁将为李宇春设计演唱会服装</b></a>｜李宇春巡回演唱会“野蛮生长”近日在北京举办发布会，宣布将由  Gucci 创意总监及 Alexander Wang 负责设计全部演出服装。</p>\n<p><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/retailing/bobbi-brown-beverly-hills-store-10463633/\">Bobbi Brown 美国开第二家店旗舰店</a></b>｜彩妆品牌 Bobbi Brown 近日在洛杉矶比佛利山庄（Beverly Hills）开旗舰店，这是品牌在美国第二家门店，也是西海岸首家。近 700 平方英尺的空间内包含 Bobbi Brown 彩妆、墨镜等全线产品。<br></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.nofashion.cn/a/1466425392606.html\"><b>剑桥包上一财年收入大跌</b></a>｜剑桥包品牌 Cambridge Satchel 宣布 2015 财年收入下跌了 25% 至 750 万英镑，不到 2013 年收入 1280 万英镑的 1/6。下滑情况开始于 2014 年获得瑞士风险投资公司 Index Ventures 的 1270 万英镑资金而大幅扩张后。创始人Julie Deane 承认在发展策略上存在失误。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">Gigi Hadid 为 Max Mara <a href=\"http://wwd.com/media-news/fashion-memopad/gallery/gigi-hadid-fronts-max-mara-accessories-ads-for-fall-10463247/#!1/gigi-hadid-in-max-mara-fw-2016-campaign/\">拍摄 2016 秋冬系列配件广告</a>：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124347Tb1Kzum9pMI7sy3N.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.43425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124348AMYc348oWdgDqCuR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57421875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124348B5ujIk0FOafMy1zr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031243491tSDyjYI8quEalZi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48828125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124349cvkoeLwmdYzstl8G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031243494yHRfGzIiFgPAjLE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">韩星权志龙（ G-Dragon）香水来一瓶？他所在的经纪公司 YG 旗下彩妆品牌 moonshot ，近日推出了为 GD 设计的中性淡香水。</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124350TxNSrPQfXuA3jYHK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124350IOVwn7kPtGelC1dU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124350A6xzOWtHeG2mYVyq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070312435113OBGsiQL2FK6qXl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"> Jimmy Choo 发布<a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/jimmy-choo-speak-choo-pre-fall-2016-campaign/\">女士 2016 早秋系列大片</a>：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031243516ves0u5RFU1XxKwT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124352FDHWTxNatRLoQ3f0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124352Ia4N9tbn70MQeRHB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">Nordstrom 百货发布波西米亚风品牌<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/free-people-nordstrom-summer-2016-outfits/\"> Free people 六月特辑</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031243539XHBUnifhryM0K1x.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77358491\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124353e6zjJRMngcqSkDOX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77358491\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124354rL0G8a5RxEtYpOI3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124354TnFfiXg7DKm1IY4c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77358491\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124355jhzyeZbLrpBcR5id.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">彩妆品牌 <a href=\"http://www.popsugar.com/beauty/Make-Up-Ever-Artist-Rouge-Collection-41548130?stream_view=1#opening-slide\">Make Up For Ever 推出全新  Artist Rouge 系列唇膏</a>，共 45 色：<br></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124355jw0zJDub7fHqstBk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124356FztlXPEfsv9gxqG5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70117188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124357io9kU2EWmcF46GB7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68066406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070312435887bqAdwWBFgEnSGt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}